    "description": "<strong>Warning!</strong><br><br>This game is currently in an unfinished state only buy it if you want to try it out.<br>I'm currently burnt out on working on this game right now, but I will continue development soon.<br><br>100% a fever dream.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175080/extras/9e0b15e403f1644c3a13429eab0094f5.avif?t=1760432649\" width=566 height=244 /></span><br><br><strong>This is a game I made for fun! Don't expect it to be the new top 10 games in the world.</strong><br><br><strong>This game is full of memes, this may or may not be the most effort I put into anything tbh.<br>made mostly for friends and family.</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175080/extras/5a317ccb4ec145648d4c3408ea52301f.avif?t=1760432649\" width=612 height=345 /></span><br><br>This game starts off in a village where you're really <strong>REALLY</strong> hungry, you decide that a banana would be the best choice of meal!<br>but sadly, and of course, the whole world is against you and your banana habit, and so your journey starts, you must go through the whole world and fight the<br>bosses and protectors of all bananas to get your hands on one.<br><br>This game has towns, dungeons, and a world map to explore!<br><br>Each area has its own set of monsters to fight.<br><br>If you encounter a monster like in RPG fashion, it's turn-based whoever has the most <strong>agility</strong> gets to go first, and some monsters can inflict <strong>status effects</strong><br>to hinder your ability to do certain things, or you can inflict good status effects on yourself! same for the monsters.<br><br>when you level up, you can gain Abilities to do certain things, such as &quot;Strong Attack&quot; which increases the damage for your attack<br> but consumes TP (Toilet Paper)<br><br>Abilities need TP or MP to use them, TP is a renewable source that you gain from getting attacked, defending and ect, MP is gained only from potions.",
